result.name: Tai Hei Cha Don

reviews.text: Fantastic, delicious HK local food restaurant
A friendly but crowded Restaurant. Economical price and the quality of food is not bad.
Small Hong Kong style cafe, nice
Delicious food and very friendly service.

Great spot for breakfast. Just a bit hard to find, though. Go down Hollywood Road and before Possession Street you'll see a Pacific Coffee. Straight before that is a lane. Turn into the lane and you'll be right there.

result.name: 大喜茶檔

reviews.text: 年輕男老闆服務快速有禮貌，座位也蠻乾淨，送湯送飲料。公司附近有空會再來。
早餐跟餐個件多士有水準
港式茶餐有家庭式親切感服務，街方熟客聚脚地，食品錯，會再光顧。
多人食既茶餐廳，有兩餸飯，水平唔差。咖哩都ok。
食物不好吃，普通九流餐廳一間。
